pull.title: qt: remove bug fix for Qt < 5.5
pull.body:
Remove the code used to fix a Qt bug in versions before Qt 5.5.0 as described in this link https://bugreports.qt.io/browse/QTBUG-43473

Now the minimum requirement is Qt 5.5.1 as described in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/dependencies.md

This code is not necessary anymore

events.body:
Concept ACK

Welcome as a contributor @10xcryptodev!

Thanks for removing old cruft! :)

ACK 514dfab03f817e806482aecdb98b77a19b6f88f8, tested on Linux Mint 19.3 with system Qt 5.9.5.

In the "Coin Selection" window with "Tree mode" set, clicking on checkbox of a parent with children set state to Qt::Checked, as expected. No regressions are found.

Just for references, history of the removed LOCs: #3846, #7334, #13458.
